      options: ["A. (a,a) вҲҲ R for all aвҲҲA", "B. (a,a) вҲү R for all aвҲҲA", "C. (a,b) вҲҲ R implies (b,a) вҲҲ R", "D. (a,b) and (b,c) implies (a,c)"],
      answer: "B. (a,a) вҲү R for all aвҲҲA",
      diff: "easy"
